  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A retro platformer with optional minor puzzle elements, alternate routes, a few roaming boss fights, and a simple but powerful item-combining system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tools and c</strong>ombining</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tools are strewn across the levels, and can be activated to 'combine' them temporarily, or combined more permanently. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For example: with a pole, activate your spring as well to instantly have a pogo stick, then also activate a spike to have a pogo-drill that destroys terrain as you bounce. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Food</strong><br>Food works in much the same way. For example: combine a leaf with meat for seasoned meats. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br>   </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A retro platformer with optional minor puzzle elements, alternate routes, a few roaming boss fights, and a simple but powerful item-combining system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tools and c</strong>ombining</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tools are strewn across the levels, and can be activated to 'combine' them temporarily, or combined more permanently. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For example: with a pole, activate your spring as well to instantly have a pogo stick, then also activate a spike to have a pogo-drill that destroys terrain as you bounce. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Food</strong><br>Food works in much the same way. For example: combine a leaf with meat for seasoned meats. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br>   </p>",
